        {
            "title": "伊朗石油出口樞紐遭襲 加劇供應中斷風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"ICE\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"615\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SORDPjUVNB4tgYTyHJjqDQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/d06a624cc9daa6121df82e7bdae4c48b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">ICE</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 承載伊朗大量石油出口的島嶼首次遭到大規模襲擊，不僅威脅到該國的命脈，也讓在持續兩周的中東衝突中，早已苦不堪言的全球供應市場陷入更深擔憂當中。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普在社交媒體上發文稱，美國轟炸了波斯灣哈爾克島上的軍事目標，但暫時放過石油基礎設施。他還警告伊朗領導人，如果干擾通過霍爾木茲海峽的船隻，他將立即重新考慮這一決定。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"698\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vKwLwSQN5sRJoffnEuHsWg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5OA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/7000e22bc319dd838986f6b37fe17203\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗嚴重依賴哈爾克島，該國十分之九的原油從這裡出口，大部分輸往中國。如果衝突升級，影響到這些原油的流通，將進一步擾亂石油市場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-205e3a73-c8df-35d3-8736-b15ec47d0011-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這很可能會削弱伊朗的出口能力，川普試圖通過升級局勢來緩和局面，」新美國安全中心的高級研究員Rachel Ziemba表示。「伊朗是否會進行報復，是石油市場和戰爭面臨的最大風險。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法新社報導，根據與革命衛隊有關的實體向當地媒體發表的評論，伊朗威脅如果該國能源設施遭到攻擊，將打擊中東與美國有關的石油目標。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"615\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tRB5FvmA1QDbiu.gFQk4dA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYxNQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/cc2f2ccd552c1f73d9b4b76bb3c9d134\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">摩根大通在3月8日的報告中指出，如果哈爾克島被迫關閉，將會迅速引發上游減產，伊朗多達一半的原油產量將面臨風險。報告稱，伊朗原本被視為將是波斯灣產油國中最晚停產的國家之一，但現在可能會早於科威特和阿聯酋。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「哈爾克島面臨美國如此直接的軍事攻擊威脅，貨輪可能會猶豫該不該裝船，」華盛頓諮詢機構Rapidan Energy Group的總裁Bob McNally說。「如果伊朗仍在干擾霍爾木茲海峽的航運，可能會更加猶豫不決。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Iran Oil Hub Strike Raises Risk of Further Disruptions to Supply</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Weilun Soon、Ari Natter.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E6%A8%9E%E7%B4%90%E9%81%AD%E8%A5%B2-%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%B7%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-052029145.html",
